I feel like I know exactly where Almost Human is headed. It’s headed to a rain-soaked Kennex cradling malfunctioning components of Dorian in his lap and screaming, “Don’t you die on me, you mechanical bastard, you’re the best goddamn partner I ever had!” Which is to say, this show might be a bit too mechanical for me. Follow @Telegraph_TV
